Pineapple can be described as a delicious tropical fruit that provides significant health benefits to the body. The benefits and reasons why you should eat pineapple more “According to a publication by Everyday health” will be discussed in this article.
1) Pineapple is an excellent source of antioxidant that fight off diseases.
2) Excellent source of vitamin C: pineapple supplies the body with a sufficient amount of vitamin C which provides antioxidant benefits and supports the immune system. Vitamin C plays an essential role in iron absorption and wound repair.
3) Promotes healthy bones: in addition to calcium, a single cup of pineapple contains 76% of the daily recommended manganese that alleviate osteoporosis.
4) Pineapples nutrient profile can boost immunity.5) Supports weight loss: pineapple is a good choice of fruit due to its low calorie content.
6) Pineapple reduces the amount of inflammation in the body.
7) Aids digestion: the bromelain in pineapple helps to improve digestion.
8) According to Mayo clinic, pineapple fights off free radicals and lowers the risk of cancer.


